{"tid":1422891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民借老豆老母手機！民間記者會最緊要入到屋！","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T12:23:19.000Z","uid":263231,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2bfb46205baaeea4545233e128fbb334df10932d","tid":1422891,"uid":263231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:16:52.000Z","msg":"民間記者會既巴絲講得幾好都好，永遠都只會係我地自己人去聽去睇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果要令民間記者會擴大影響力，就一定要令佢入到屋<br />\n有一堆人始終永遠都只係會睇TVB <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我諗左幾個方法，大家一齊討論下：<br />\n<br />\n1）民間放映會要做 <br />\n落去社區，港鐵站門口不停咁播，係會有廢老停低睇嫁<br />\n去社區做放映會，效果分分鐘好過你日日去唔同區開狗開拖，幾咁和理非 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2）借老豆老母手機 <br />\nLog in 佢Whatsapp web wechat web 幫佢瘋狂forward d 精華呀 警察點打老人家呀 小朋友果d片出去 務求要佢手機每個人都收到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3) 要電台播！<br />\n好多的士司機唯一娛樂就係電台！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家仲諗到乜，一齊討論下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed926472e96047a0d4f01a595c8f79f734cc8a30","tid":1422891,"uid":294614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:23:06.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3876991fcd935f627cae39199e8fc65dd7c74b04","tid":1422891,"uid":294614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:23:19.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}